{"type":"text","timestamp":1773433472820,"sessionID":"ses_31723c227ffes6YQhTzXCb8Yyr","part":{"id":"prt_ce8df20b0001zt0ktjPO5ReU7R","sessionID":"ses_31723c227ffes6YQhTzXCb8Yyr","messageID":"msg_ce8df1740001tdno1VTZZam62s","type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### Files Changed\n1. **`tests/worktree-filtering.test.ts`** (new, 550 lines) — Comprehensive integration tests using real temporary git repositories\n2. **`src/lib/worktree.ts`** (1 line changed) — Exported `verifyConfigFiles` for testability\n\n### Test Coverage (28 tests, all passing)\n\n**`listWomboWorktrees` — real git integration (7 tests)**\n- Empty worktree list, matching/non-matching prefixes\n- **Critical**: Project root exclusion when name starts with prefix (\"woco-something\" with \"woco-\" prefix)\n- **Critical**: Classic \"wombo-combo\" with \"wombo-\" prefix collision\n- Custom prefix support, mixed prefix scenarios\n\n**`removeWorktree` — safety guard (7 tests)**\n- Refuses project root removal (exact match, resolved paths, trailing slash)\n- Refuses removal when project root name starts with prefix\n- Successfully removes legitimate worktrees\n- Branch deletion toggle (deleteBranchToo flag)\n\n**`cleanupAllWorktrees` — selective cleanup (5 tests)**\n- Removes all matching worktrees, skips non-matching\n- **Critical**: Never removes project root even when name starts with prefix\n- Returns correct count, handles empty/no-match cases\n\n**`verifyConfigFiles` — config verification (5 tests)**\n- No warnings when all config files present\n- Warns about missing config files\n- Skips non-existent source files, handles empty config list\n- Detects missing directory config files\n\n**`createWorktree` — config copying integration (1 test)**\n- Verifies config files are actually copied with correct content\n\n**Prefix edge cases (3 tests)**\n- Substring prefix mismatch, exact prefix match, project root exactly matching prefix","time":{"start":1773433472818,"end":1773433472818}}}
